title: Mid Rise Luxury Memorial Park living-Up Two Weeks Free
posting_body: ['For leasing info call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#734292', 'Nestled between the Heights, Rice Military and Memorial Park, you’ll be conveniently near the many retailers and restaurants of Washington Avenue and the employment destinations of Midtown/Downtown, all just minutes away.', 'Thoughtfully designed amenity spaces and curated interior finishes provide a welcoming home at this community.', "With the essential items you expect and amazing offerings that never fail to impress, such as a comfortable pet spa and an outstanding fitness center, what you'll experience will be exceptional as much for what’s available for you here as for the opportunity to enjoy it all in such a brilliant community environment.", 'See the complete lists below.', 'Community Features:', 'Expansive pool with gathering cabana and outdoor grilling areas', 'Pet friendly community with dog spa and pet park', 'Roof deck with outdoor kitchen and views of Downtown and Memorial Park', 'Multi use amenity area with: 24/7/365 Fitness center with Precor touchscreen theater cardio equipment, multifunctional training station with slam balls, battle ropes and conditioning equipment, free weights and Reflect virtual training mirrors', '24/7/365 Package lockers with refrigerated storage units', 'Coworking spaces and flexible gathering areas with treelined views', 'Putting green with lounge and refreshment bar', 'Proximity to Memorial Park and Memorial Park golf course']
